                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10225" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-1170</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">189 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“机”不可失，“械”甲归田——钵施然边疆农业智能装备的技术赶超之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Seize the Machine Opportunity, Let Mechanics Serve the Fields——The Path of Boshiran’s Technological Catch-Up in Frontier Agricultural Equipment</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">徐攀，王溢谦，张定鹏，潘懿歆，叶凡</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浙江工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新疆钵施然智能农机股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">研发部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">19 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">技术赶超；农业机械化；技术破局；市场突围；生态合围；2025百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Technology catching-up, Agricultural Mechanization, Technological Breakthrough, Market Breakout, Ecological Encirclement</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">面对进口品牌垄断采棉机市场、新疆棉农劳动强度大且效率低下的困境，钵施然农业科技有限公司以技术赶超为核心，从本土化需求出发，实现了采棉机从“卡脖子”到“中国方案”的技术突破和超越。本案例以公司创业历程为主线：首先分析钵施然的创立背景，揭示棉田机械化需求与技术垄断的矛盾；其次分别从技术路径、市场路径、产业路径阐述钵施然对国外采棉机的赶超过程；最后展望企业在国际市场中的未来发展。本案例旨在引导学生思考后发农业装备企业如何根据内部资源和外部环境，选择合适的赶超时机、战略和路径，从而提升企业的追赶绩效，为农业智能装备行业的技术赶超提供借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Faced with the challenges of international brands monopolizing the cotton picker market and the high labor intensity and low efficiency of cotton farmers in Xinjiang, Boshiran Agricultural Technology Co., Ltd. has focused on technological advancement as its core strategy. By addressing localized needs, the company has achieved a technological breakthrough in cotton pickers, transforming from a “bottleneck constraint” to a “Chinese solution”. This case study traces the company’s entrepreneurial journey: First, it analyzes the founding background of Boshiran, highlighting the contradiction between the demand for mechanization in cotton fields and technological monopolies. Next, it elaborates on Boshiran’s catch-up process with foreign cotton pickers from three perspectives—technological path, market path, and industrial path. Finally, it explores the company’s future development in the global market. The case aims to guide students in analyzing how latecomer agricultural machinery enterprises can leverage internal resources and external environments to select appropriate timing, strategies, and pathways for technological catch-up, thereby enhancing their catch-up performance and providing insights for the agricultural intelligent equipment industry.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业战略管理》、《创新管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">技术赶超时机；赶超战略；赶超路径；赶超绩效</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-12</td>
                            </tr>
